{"type": "article", "id": 18807, "title": "华沙电影节门票海报", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-10T07:30:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 28, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607102436ehoLflduBzxWi2Dq.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这套电影节的门票及海报的设计是基于柯布西耶的 Modulor 理论。波兰的设计事务所 UVMW 将用来计算人像比例的圆实体化，分割成红蓝两色，然后任意排列。大大小小的红蓝色半圆在白纸上跳跃着，保留了人体的感觉，又带有很强的几何感。这组元素运用在了海报、门票和纪念包上，也是纪念柯布西耶逝世五十周年。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607102434CFXBSdwWRE25Q7Hf.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.51709402\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060710243427reLoAOQw0B9xya.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.41559829\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607102435eIkh7WKymM39qnlu.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.63354701\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607102435tAcxW2NaJdL7fymV.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}